text: Subsequentis to them nos sent noster messengers. Nos sent Jesus filius Mary nos dedit eum Injeel (Gospel) nos locus hearts de his followers kindness mercy. they invented hermitism nos nunquam decretum them. totus nos asked them perfecit est uphold commandments approved DEUS! they non uphold message prout they habet. Consequently nos dedit those believed them their recompense dum multus de them est wicked
